1. output required variables on pressure levels, e.g. via VAXTRA
   - temperature
   - u-wind
   - v-wind
   - vertical velocity

2. ./configure [... options ...]
   gmake tools
      OR
   gmake tools target=temdiag

3. adapt temdiag.nml according to the dimension and dimension variable names
   and copy/link it to the data directory

4. <path to>/.../bin/temdiag.exe input.nc output.nc
